{
  "stem": "8370.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They are surrounded by the SS people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They brought them-- they divided them in, I would say, section of 20, 30.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They brought them into the big house opposite in the yard behind the houses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we heard was a shooting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Da-da-da-da-da.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the SS came out, has taken the second group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was women, children, different ages, you know, men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Again, in the doorway, deep in the yard, and again the shooting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so it was a couple of time, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was just, I would say, two days-- this fact happened about two days before we left for Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in this prison, I was two months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two months.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then on 29th of April, they brought us in the morning into the trucks who arrive in the yard of the prison, loaded on the trucks, and to the railway station on the-- it was not the main railway station of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was on outskirt of Warsaw-- loaded into the cattle trucks about 50, 60 for each cattle truck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the way between the prison and the railway station, we saw the burned houses and plenty of corpses on the street in the ghetto, killed people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we arrive on the 29 of April, '43 to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was not the main camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cattle truck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Railway truck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are not aware where we are going, which direction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We understood, looking on the, through the small windows, on the station, on the road, that we are going southwest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But where?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not aware.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
